            <div class="bk2 bkgr"><span class="bktm">12:00 pm</span>Midday break</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkg"><span class="bktm">1:00 pm</span>Rep 1:1 · introductory conversation (rep 2)</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkb"><span class="bktm">2:30 pm</span>Customer ride-along · listen for expansion signals</div>
