        </div>
        <div class="note-box"><strong style="color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;">Month 1 focus:</strong> Every week in days 1–30 is about absorbing and orienting. Tuesday through Thursday are for customer calls and ride-alongs. Monday is for internal rhythm and leadership meetings. Friday is for thinking, synthesis and wrapping up with time left to breathe before the weekend.</div>
      </div>
      <div id="m2" class="mo">
