            <div class="bk2 bkgr"><span class="bktm">12:00 pm</span>Midday break</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkb"><span class="bktm">1:00 pm</span>Customer call · Source cross-sell conversation</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkn"><span class="bktm">2:30 pm</span>Monthly mentor check-in</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkg"><span class="bktm">3:30 pm</span>1:1 with rep 4 · pipeline and development</div>
