          </div></div>
          <div class="dc2"><div class="dh dhf">Friday</div><div class="db">
            <div class="bk2 bkt"><span class="bktm">8:30 am</span>Leadership sync with D'Arcy · week debrief</div>
            <div class="bk2 bko"><span class="bktm">9:30 am</span>Pipegen and value capture concept · account plans and win story review</div>
            <div class="bk2 bka"><span class="bktm">10:30 am</span>Enablement · post-Engage AI messaging and product deep-dive</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkgr"><span class="bktm">12:00 pm</span>Midday break</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkp"><span class="bktm">1:00 pm</span>Weekly team performance summary and forecast narrative draft</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkn"><span class="bktm">2:00 pm</span>Coffee chat · cross-functional relationship build</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkgr"><span class="bktm">3:00 pm</span>Personal time · log off</div>
          </div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="note-box"><strong style="color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;">Month 2 focus:</strong> Tuesday through Thursday are fully customer-facing with onsites as the priority. The team tools session and first prospecting exercise happen this month. Mondays are for internal rhythm, forecast prep and 1:1s. Fridays are for thinking, leadership prep and cross-functional relationship building.</div>
      </div>
      <div id="m3" class="mo">
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#5f5e5a;margin-bottom:10px;font-weight:500;">Typical week · Days 61–90 · Accelerate, own, capitalize on Engage momentum</div>
        <div class="cg5">
          <div class="dc2"><div class="dh dhm">Monday</div><div class="db">
            <div class="bk2 bkp"><span class="bktm">8:00 am</span>Morning brief · weekly priority setting</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkt"><span class="bktm">9:00 am</span>Weekly team meeting · Engage learnings debrief and thought leadership brief</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkt"><span class="bktm">10:00 am</span>Leadership forecast call · present team number</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkt"><span class="bktm">11:00 am</span>QBR prep session with D'Arcy</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkgr"><span class="bktm">12:30 pm</span>Midday break</div>
            <div class="bk2 bko"><span class="bktm">1:30 pm</span>Pipegen and prospecting strategy · post-Engage follow-up review</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkg"><span class="bktm">2:30 pm</span>1:1 with rep 5 · pipeline, coaching and win story status</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkg"><span class="bktm">3:30 pm</span>New rep ramp review · is each on track</div>
          </div></div>
          <div class="dc2"><div class="dh dht">Tuesday</div><div class="db">
            <div class="bk2 bkp"><span class="bktm">8:00 am</span>Thought leadership outreach drafts · personalized per account</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkb"><span class="bktm">9:00 am</span>Customer call · post-Engage thought leadership follow-up</div>
