            <div class="bk2 bkp"><span class="bktm">1:00 pm</span>Win story documentation from onsite</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkb"><span class="bktm">2:30 pm</span>Customer call · exec relationship follow-up</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkg"><span class="bktm">4:00 pm</span>1:1 with rep 6 · post-Engage pipeline and account plan review</div>
          </div></div>
          <div class="dc2"><div class="dh dhw">Wednesday</div><div class="db">
            <div class="bk2 bkp"><span class="bktm">8:00 am</span>Morning brief and prep</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkb"><span class="bktm">9:00 am</span>Customer call · Source expansion conversation</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkt"><span class="bktm">10:00 am</span>AM/RM joint account review · renewal timing and growth plays</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkgr"><span class="bktm">12:00 pm</span>Midday break</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkb"><span class="bktm">1:00 pm</span>Customer onsite · post-Engage relationship deepening</div>
            <div class="bk2 bka"><span class="bktm">3:30 pm</span>Team workshop · prospecting exercise and win story sharing</div>
            <div class="bk2 bkp"><span class="bktm">4:30 pm</span>Post-onsite follow-up and win story capture</div>
          </div></div>
          <div class="dc2"><div class="dh dhth">Thursday</div><div class="db">
            <div class="bk2 bkp"><span class="bktm">8:00 am</span>Account briefs and post-Engage strategy prep</div>
